  "new_regression_audit": {
    "question": "Do the real CD steps in models NOT in R1/R2/R3 (GPTNeo, DistilBert, DebertaV2, TrOCR, XGLM, vit_dinov2, deit_base, densenet, phlippe, ghostnet, repvgg, Blenderbot, MobileBert, visformer, Albert, nfnet) constitute NEW unaccounted model-level regressions?",
